WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:26.550 --> 00:00:32.022
鉄で出来た凹凸の街で
In this rugged iron city,  

00:00:32.795 --> 00:00:38.265
ずっと見慣れた夢も　枯れそう
the dreams I'm used to seeing always wither.

00:00:38.264 --> 00:00:41.625
交差点はこもれ陽で揺らいだ　
Wavering amidst the sifted sunlight, 

00:00:41.639 --> 00:00:44.626
途方にくれて見失う道
I become lost at an intersection.

00:00:44.625 --> 00:00:47.737
サヨナラをたくさん思い出して　
Suddenly I remember all the goodbyes 

00:00:47.736 --> 00:00:52.594
ふいに浮かぶメロディー
and I am flooded with memories.

00:01:03.990 --> 00:01:09.435
とても輝いて見える空を
The shining sky glistens 

00:01:10.178 --> 00:01:15.727
錆びたブランコこいで仰ぐ
from where I gaze on this rusted swing.

00:01:15.726 --> 00:01:18.831
流れてく雲はなんか叙情的
I always stare at the blue cracks  

00:01:18.845 --> 00:01:22.073
隙間の青をずっと眺めた
peaking between the story-telling clouds

00:01:22.073 --> 00:01:25.285
舞いあがって思いも投げたら
If I could throw my feelings into the air,

00:01:25.285 --> 00:01:28.245
憂い消えた
my sadness would fade

00:01:28.623 --> 00:01:34.908
風が変わって　冷たい季節の予感で
The change in wind is the beginning of a cold season

00:01:34.907 --> 00:01:41.263
グルグル回る　切ない心飛ばされて
My wounded heart flies in circles

00:01:41.277 --> 00:01:47.587
漂いながら　君にまで届けばいいな
I wish it could reach you as it floats

00:01:47.586 --> 00:01:55.366
僕だけの花　季節はずれた咲いたらいいな
Only my flower blooms out of season

00:01:55.471 --> 00:02:04.321
未来まで透けるような、寒い空ーー。
The cold sky shows through to the future--.

00:02:15.632 --> 00:02:21.399
言葉つむいで作る希望　
My hopes and words are stitched together

00:02:21.916 --> 00:02:27.511
明日を手さぐりでまた探す
I search and fumble my way into tomorrow

00:02:27.524 --> 00:02:30.559
色つけずに世界を描いた　
I paint a world 

00:02:30.572 --> 00:02:33.714
君を描く絵の具だけ残してさ
where only you have color

00:02:33.710 --> 00:02:36.909
出来たらすぐ見せに行かなくちゃ
I have to show you as soon as I can 

00:02:36.922 --> 00:02:39.985
褪せる前に
before it fades

00:02:40.190 --> 00:02:46.547
風が変わって　冷たい季節の匂いで
The change in wind smells like a cold season

00:02:46.578 --> 00:02:52.999
